Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:51.44,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an9}捕捉那交錯的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:56.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}拜託了  Bitter  Tune
