Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的那個看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了看了  很有趣啊  真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}露臍裝有著秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}心型項鏈是秘密道具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨拙女孩小秋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好  乃木坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香是走路上學的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是有車接送呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  因為很近嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  走路有益健康
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:00:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:00:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕  不可饒恕  不可饒恕…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  剛才用手機看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  這是笨拙女孩小秋的官方網站啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我也瞭解一下春香喜歡的動畫比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎  我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子是沒用女孩小惠  應該說是小秋的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨裕人  不可饒恕  不可饒恕…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  乃木坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉住他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起  我太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡秋葉原系這件事是秘密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  是我和裕人之間的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這個  這個星期天有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼特別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那樣的話  能…能不能和我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能和我一起出去？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}註：「陪我一起」和「與我交往」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個難道是約會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪裡是什麼約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只…只是有東西想買  如果可以陪我一起去的話我會很感激的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想世上一般來說把這就叫約會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎  謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個地方是第一次去  一個人比較不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想著要是被拒絕了的話該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  一個人？  難道說買東西是去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  是去秋葉原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋…秋葉原  那裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼裕人  我再去逛幾家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊信長  這個要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有很珍貴的書  要小心點拿回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我再也不來了  秋葉原這種鬼地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那以後  就沒再來過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  讓你久等了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我也剛到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉原的車站裡真混亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這麼盯著我看的話總覺得…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對…對不起  不自覺地就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不配
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是名優嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  去買東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,購物導遊圖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導遊圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  上面整合了今天的預計路線和目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了製作這個花了我三小時哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逛這裡  這裡  還有這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也逛一逛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終目的地是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PDS？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我無論如何都想買那叫\N「Portable  Dream  Station」的新款手掌遊戲機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  這個是熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是貓咪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…對啊  是貓咪啊貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這隻貓咪畫得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然自賣自誇很不好意思  但這可是我很有自信的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我想這是非常有衝擊力的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  哇  好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是第一次給別人看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為春香什麼都那麼完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來不擅長畫畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨拙  笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}咦？  笨拙女孩和沒用女孩誰更可靠…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不先去買PDS什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因為一開始就去買的話  就完成目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得出來購物  這樣太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我想把最高興的事留到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  首先是這家店  虎之穴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  我還是第一次看到這麼多同人志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同人志？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣以動畫或者遊戲的人物當藍本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再自己創作出來的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}右下角方框的字是：那樣的話我就做個基男給你看\N  直到世界毀滅之前都會為了姐姐大人而活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是animate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  有這麼多動畫周邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  這個好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  到下一個地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  什麼都不買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  應該是這前面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人看看  很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的東西光看看就有很幸福的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊  那麼喜歡的話買下不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很想買下來  但是預算不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的爸爸非常嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用在這種興趣上的零花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天帶來的也是為了這一天而存下來的重要的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此  小豬上了天國
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小豬？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒關係  光是這樣看一下我就非常滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  春香為什麼會喜歡上秋葉原系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊  已經是五六年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為被爸爸責罵而在公園裡哭泣的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個不認識的男孩子送了我一本書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  難道說那本書是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  「innocent  SMILE」的創刊號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我以前從未看過這類書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但等回過神來的時侯  已經完全陷進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何時已經忘了被責罵時的辛酸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧  漫畫啊動畫之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？裕人  喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信長？！糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  對不起  稍微躲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇啊  裕人竟然會來秋葉原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面的興趣終於覺醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  要說起來的話本來就是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  這種事現在再說也沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那種事  你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話  說到秋葉原就有我  說到我就有秋葉原
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不久後在Soft  One有DVD發售活動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}Soft  One（Soft  One  to  Threre）：\N秋葉原地區石丸電器一家分店，販賣CD、DVD、遊戲、動畫等相關產品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎  那就不該在這種地方扯了啊  快點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是還有時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  在這裡廢話的話就搶不到好位置了哦  快走快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也對  那再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我跟你女朋友打聲招呼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  讓你久等了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？春香？不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  這裡誰也沒有啦  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣的人群裡亂跑  真沒常識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我並不是故意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  對不起  我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我在找一個大小姐模樣的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  和女朋友走散了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友  朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是不是有在想「她是女朋友該多好」？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並…並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害羞  不要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的那種女孩剛才我看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在那邊的巷子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拼命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不…不是的  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人似乎迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為語言不通正在為難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就給他們帶路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  小姐  莫非這位是你的男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎把你們當成壞人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是這樣呢  再見  boy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  要保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點小事情  不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是春香  真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思裕人  什麼也沒說就走開了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來接下來去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  早就想去那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭蛋機會館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是小秋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要試試嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  試試是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  扭蛋很便宜的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我  那個…是第一次的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過春香的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是看還是碰  都是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  這時候應該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然應該說是  初體驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初…初…  雖然說的沒錯但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  試一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心  很簡單  不要害怕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  那就嘗試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回一定…嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎出來的都是不想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回一定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又是相同的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…春香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  扭蛋是靠運氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  接下來是去@home  cafe吃午飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  接下來去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是  說的是  打起精神去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看上去是普通的店  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  菜單很可愛哦  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  原來如此  果然很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  大小姐  你們要點什麼菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍微等…一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\fad(200,200)}註：@home  cafe是秋葉原著名女僕咖啡廳，\N還組織過「完全メイド宣言」等藝術團體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼進去的時候沒有發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是吧  太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點  男朋友翹首以待著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  店裡的女僕說無論如何也想叫我穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要那…那樣盯著人家看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會…會不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點  男朋友  這種時候要好好稱讚一下女朋友的可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真可愛  不過我不是男朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別害羞  別害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  靠近點  靠近點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要照了哦  看這裡  看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備  萌萌笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得真是壯烈吶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害羞的  不過其實是很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也拍了照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是時候進行今天的主要活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去買Portable  Dream  Station
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's  go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8768E1&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(200,200)}本日已售完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(500,200)}進貨日未定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不好意思  上午就全賣光了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡都是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  只能等下次了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an8}註：背景牆壁上貼著的是夏娜S2卷小說封面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  我們太小看銷售速度了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  稍微忍一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既沒達到目的  還給裕人帶來這麼多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像沒用女孩小惠一樣沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話還不如不來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人也是這樣想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天都和春香在一起到處逛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了很多東西  真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和春香兩人之間的秘密  又多了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和裕人一起出來  真的是很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:20:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻甩下裕人  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前好像也發生過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  誰啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上給我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃螃蟹！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我收到了撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  那個  謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福我又恢復了點精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那麼回車站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}註：木板上的字是「請小心變態」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑他人的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不  我沒笑  我沒笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在笑  都笑得一塌糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  因為  春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分  真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  春香你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後再來玩一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是嘲笑你的賠禮  我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這個姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨拙女孩小秋的招牌動作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把這東西當成寶物的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個姿勢很可愛我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是裕人送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只憑這一點這就是我非常非常重要的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.29,0:22:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  那個  怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下…下次再來一起買PDS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的  一定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.51,0:22:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一起…來秋葉原
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.21,0:24:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨裕人到乃木坂家作客
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是與普通生活的離別之曲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是被女僕們玩弄的光景開啟了新的時代嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.66,0:24:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  完蛋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.95,0:24:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了時代的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.00,0:24:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我的台詞呢
